{"tid":806713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中 國 農 莊","createTime":"2018-09-05T02:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T07:20:06.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d149291136e393d9af4228fa0a302878d3992c8","tid":806713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180905/large/e8811a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180905%2Flarge%2Fe8811a.jpg&h=52166200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回教一年一度的麥加朝聖期八月二十四日告終，其間中國大陸回民赴麥加者，不少須戴上中共特製追蹤器「朝覲通」，方便當局監視其一舉一動。今天，農人或會把定位追蹤器裝在牲畜身上，以防走失。中共不把朝覲通稱為牲畜定位追蹤器，是不把回民視同家畜，的確尊重民權。<br />\n<br />\n當然，名稱可以不同，牧民與牧畜，對中共來說，其實差不多。繁殖就是一例。牲畜要不育，則閹之；要多出，則不妨強令交配、受精等。新中國人之繁殖，最近四十年就是如此：一九七九年，中共患人口太多，於是開始厲行一孩政策，婦女如有不從，懷第二胎，必須「打下來，墮出來，流出來，就是不能生下來」。而一家多生，或株連鄰里，所謂「一人超生，全村結紮」是也。據統計，一九八零至二零一四年間，婦女給抓去強迫戴上子宮環者，人數達三億二千四百萬。多生孩子的家庭還要罰款，名曰「社會撫養費」。<br />\n<br />\n但是，到了二零一五年，中共發覺治下人口不足，新中國這個大農莊缺乏勞動力，於是宣布廢除一孩政策；次年，又宣布將為一千八百萬有繁殖力婦女除去子宮環；最近，更有中共學者劉志彪、胡繼曄等倡議，任何夫婦不配合習主席民族偉大復興大計，不生兩個勞動力，就要罰款，名曰「生育基金」。誰說中國農莊的動物不是都站起來了。<br />\n<br />\n古德明 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20180905/20491941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180905%2F20491941&d=475R2aNBn2CFmojb1lVusZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=40ac4aa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180905%2F20491941&h=43ff3de0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20180905/20491941</a>"},{"pid":"847437a4a7a3be0eaf3a7e60386007f935d8fd0f","tid":806713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"連登仔：今次就撐中共喇"},{"pid":"700927067185204257770ffd1948236ddab24cae","tid":806713,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df82371ec759ea0646266375cd115cd0672920d6","tid":806713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705bf0bb3a9a0c672c6fdbd48f9d3f67f159f25c","tid":806713,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/110553_f6e67df17d1ab191f4c5e9280d998478.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F110553_f6e67df17d1ab191f4c5e9280d998478.png&h=bc253156&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e90c9ed7ff5af0228f766eb79fcd79f79f1b365","tid":806713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.popdaily.com.tw/static/article/21596/GwXYHKJVz59idaSJgM5FAdHa0TKR36DYn24m2gyw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.popdaily.com.tw%2Fstatic%2Farticle%2F21596%2FGwXYHKJVz59idaSJgM5FAdHa0TKR36DYn24m2gyw.png&h=5531181a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}